# Archives
# ============================================
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.rar

# ============================================
# Project-Specific
# ============================================
# CLI output
cli-output/
validation-reports/

# Runtime data
captured-data/temp/

# ============================================
# Claude Code Configuration
# ============================================
# Exclude Claude Code settings files
**/settings.json
**/settings.local.json
../../settings.json
../../settings.local.json

# Exclude other Claude directories
**/commands/
../../commands/

# ============================================
# Keep These Files
# ============================================
!.gitignore
!.gitkeep
!README.md
!LICENSE
!SKILL.md
